{"tid":974641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報—支持台灣獨立","createTime":"2019-01-09T04:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T10:55:59.000Z","uid":17641,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3a9f327de49d259db9022ea8ae71c8cfe3207ab","tid":974641,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"戰後國民政府接管台灣，1947年台灣爆發二二八事件，中共的《解放日報》還在三月八日發表「支持台灣獨立」的言論。毛澤東在延安的廣播講話就說：「我們中國共產黨所領導的武裝部隊，完全支援台灣人民反對蔣介石和國民黨的鬥爭。我們贊成台灣獨立，我們贊成台灣自己成立一個自己所要求的國家。」"},{"pid":"6edd026fb2dbc1e7fd7370730969d82bbf98c251","tid":974641,"uid":172244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T04:45:42.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"de17746372177e995fd7d5806be210f2f2f24afe","tid":974641,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"🤔"},{"pid":"de1414351e4c857ac7e91a9e1a6b9772f5add7e7","tid":974641,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:52:52.000Z","msg":"嗱老衲 呢鋪我就撐你啦"},{"pid":"fc81275ffc9599a354ba5dbd279783e126220ea1","tid":974641,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"難得高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313268073967fed5c3de52b0f06d01fe8e164acb","tid":974641,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"應該係講：當時鼓吹台灣親共人士「獨立成國」，然後與大陸統一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0226549703bea5be9f09cf39f3fb89b4381b6e6","tid":974641,"uid":33631,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:58:27.000Z","msg":"解放日報定人民日報呀？"},{"pid":"b4610626b0be267c9a3ab88a3d3e6fbcc6109d2f","tid":974641,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:58:35.000Z","msg":"一國兩制都可以推翻，更唔好話老毛年代既說話啦"},{"pid":"097f6d9a6221127b6fb0571799d3565a3eab4cfa","tid":974641,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep